he same.\n\n  * I was able to read your personal emails and all the server logs, also all the files uploaded by others and admins. I was also able to join a ticket due to an email which leaked the joining link.\nThe irony is I was also able to read the email sent by Hackerone support to start this program :D\n\nNo harm has been done, you can remove the screenshots from here after you fix this bug.\n\n## Supporting Material/References:\n\n  * Have attached all the screenshots below which shows how harmful this could have been.\n\n## Impact\n\nAll the files on the server are being leaked incuding personal emails and logs.","weakness":{"id":26,"name":"Improper Access Control - Generic"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":292203,"file_name":"Screen_Shot_2018-05-01_at_1.05.13_AM.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/000/292/203/05bd3fa046e5355f0aca1dd75b36fc563c7916d2/Screen_Shot_2018-05-01_at_1.05.13_AM.png?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Screen_Shot_2018-05-01_at_1.05.13_AM.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Screen_Shot_2018-05-01_at_1.05.13_AM.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQQJGGPZOK%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T093921Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECgaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJGMEQCIFRoAkK2pIoeVGJggpRS3B%2FoVx5w%2B%2FZX6d2wSeXuXd%2FYAiAT7vegUQKGuzO78%2BbrWzHyxesFEpwqQsp6pj0Y7gZ9Uiq7BQjx%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F8BEAMaDDAxMzYxOTI3NDg0OSIMTy0ynErS6iTFn%2BkpKo8F3cheRObzYv0gbwBUz%2B3MVI6c45pZ9CCyuHtuRZclI0PFK9NtYlHjI54GUsLtROyQREZvmbZWJUtdhkYzD0wAJgVz8Onb9BiGi%2B%2FemsI6fX64tZJTXchenfQhzpdWlwlq3ddAcz8%2Fg9pSE8%2FXRdqKlkHIXXimhHTRFvM8NTVgkICpR%2F1B%2FMH%2ByuWQmo2VLYjQlP50CxvRfGzUO6Ky6Tk1SskZa4l7zDrTfYkaFSSO1czWhxEPP8fTUM8KYoeohbGilZ1xexgyCqM%2B5rCsNyJnIWVGaabx%2BdArs7F9ZLf4b%2FjjUH8QsYppF6vbkLwN4